[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     16[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe has no CRITICAL findings and 2 HIGH findings. Both are addressable with targeted additions. The architecture is sound for the stated use case, the HIPAA considerations are mostly well-handled, and the domain treatment is accurate. The geocoding quality discussion and equity considerations are particular strengths.
