[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    138[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Fix:** Clarify: "Use S3 and DynamoDB Gateway endpoints (free, no per-GB charge). Use Interface endpoints for CloudWatch Logs. Gateway endpoints are sufficient for batch pipeline access patterns and avoid the hourly + data processing charges of Interface endpoints."
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    139[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
